Title: Technoscrying: Observatory
Description:
My dowsing rods have been pointing towards a set of Drakonid ruins atop a cliff in Waking Shores.

I know not what we'll find, but it's never wise to question the whims of my inventions. They're always 97% correct. 

Always.
ObjectivesText: Meet Zenata at the Concord Observatory in Waking Shores.
